<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><!DOCTYPE article  PUBLIC "-//NLM//DTD Journal Publishing DTD v3.0 20080202//EN" "http://dtd.nlm.nih.gov/publishing/3.0/journalpublishing3.dtd"><article xmlns:mml="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" dtd-version="3.0" xml:lang="en" article-type="research article"><front><journal-meta><journal-id journal-id-type="publisher-id">PM</journal-id><journal-title-group><journal-title>Pure  Mathematics</journal-title></journal-title-group><issn pub-type="epub">2160-7583</issn><publisher><publisher-name>Scientific Research Publishing</publisher-name></publisher></journal-meta><article-meta><article-id pub-id-type="doi">10.12677/PM.2017.75046</article-id><article-id pub-id-type="publisher-id">PM-21747</article-id><article-categories><subj-group subj-group-type="heading"><subject>PM20170500000_42287448.pdf</subject></subj-group><subj-group subj-group-type="Discipline-v2"><subject>数学与物理</subject></subj-group></article-categories><title-group><article-title>
 
 
  交换环上线性群中含根子群的极大子群
  Maximal Subgroups Containing Root Subgroups in Linear Groups over Commutative Ring
 
</article-title></title-group><contrib-group><contrib contrib-type="author" xlink:type="simple"><name name-style="western"><surname>侯</surname><given-names>欣</given-names></name><xref ref-type="aff" rid="aff1"><sup>1</sup></xref><xref ref-type="corresp" rid="cor1"><sup>*</sup></xref></contrib><contrib contrib-type="author" xlink:type="simple"><name name-style="western"><surname>李</surname><given-names>尚志</given-names></name><xref ref-type="aff" rid="aff2"><sup>2</sup></xref><xref ref-type="aff" rid="aff1"><sup>1</sup></xref></contrib></contrib-group><aff id="aff2"><addr-line>null</addr-line></aff><aff id="aff1"><addr-line>北京航空航天大学数学与系统科学学院，北京</addr-line></aff><author-notes><corresp id="cor1">* E-mail:<email>houge19870512@126.com(侯欣)</email>;</corresp></author-notes><pub-date pub-type="epub"><day>21</day><month>08</month><year>2017</year></pub-date><volume>07</volume><issue>05</issue><fpage>363</fpage><lpage>367</lpage><permissions><copyright-statement>&#169; Copyright  2014 by authors and Scientific Research Publishing Inc. </copyright-statement><copyright-year>2014</copyright-year><license><license-p>This work is licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution International License (CC BY). http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/</license-p></license></permissions><abstract><p>
 
 
   
   本文验证了交换环上线性群中三种含根子群的子群的极大性，并讨论了交换环上线性群中含根子群的极大子群的可能类型。 The maximality of three types of subgroups containing root subgroups in linear groups is verified in this paper. And the possible types of maximal subgroups containing root subgroups in linear groups over commutative ring are discussed.
    
  
 
</p></abstract><kwd-group><kwd>极大子群，根子群，线性群，交换环, Maximal Subgroups</kwd><kwd> Root Subgroups</kwd><kwd> Linear Groups</kwd><kwd> Commutative Ring</kwd></kwd-group></article-meta></front><body><sec id="s1"><title>交换环上线性群中含根子群的极大子群<sup> </sup></title><p>侯欣<sup>*</sup>，李尚志</p><p>北京航空航天大学数学与系统科学学院，北京</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.21747-formula3"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x5_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>收稿日期：2017年8月3日；录用日期：2017年8月17日；发布日期：2017年8月21日</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.21747-formula4"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x6_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula></sec><sec id="s2"><title>摘 要</title><p>本文验证了交换环上线性群中三种含根子群的子群的极大性，并讨论了交换环上线性群中含根子群的极大子群的可能类型。</p><p>关键词 :极大子群，根子群，线性群，交换环</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.21747-formula5"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x7_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>Copyright &#169; 2017 by authors and Hans Publishers Inc.</p><p>This work is licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution International License (CC BY).</p><p>http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/</p><p><img src="http://image.hanspub.org:8080\Html/htmlimages\1-2890033x\e70a10f1-7c93-45ea-9603-062237856e4b.png" /><img src="http://image.hanspub.org:8080\Html\htmlimages\1-2890033x\e898c85e-ffc4-45c9-b817-14224a4d6960.png" /></p></sec><sec id="s3"><title>1. 引言</title><p>典型群的极大子群是群论研究的一个重要课题。作为一类特殊的极大子群，含根子群的极大子群也得到了广泛的研究。文献 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.21747-ref1">1</xref>] 中作者给出了域上线性群中含根子群的几类子群的极大性证明，并证明了域上线性群中含根子群的极大子群必属于这几类极大子群之一。辛群中含根子群的极大子群的研究可参见 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.21747-ref2">2</xref>] [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.21747-ref3">3</xref>] [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.21747-ref4">4</xref>] 。酉群中含根子群的极大子群的研究可参见 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.21747-ref5">5</xref>] [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.21747-ref6">6</xref>] 。正交群中含根子群的极大子群的研究可参见 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.21747-ref7">7</xref>] 。本文主要研究交换环上线性群中含根子群的极大子群。</p><p>设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x10_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是含幺交换环，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x11_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x12_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>分别是<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x13_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>上的一般线性群和特殊线性群。设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x14_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是单位阵，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x15_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>表示第<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x16_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>位置为1，其余位置为0的<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x17_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>阶方阵，一般线性群<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x18_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>中的所有初等平延</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.21747-formula6"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x19_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>生成一个子群<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x20_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，它是<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x21_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的一个子群。事实上，域<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x22_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>上有<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x23_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。容易验证</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.21747-formula7"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x24_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>也是<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x25_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的一个子群，我们把这样的子群以及它们在<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x26_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>中的共轭子群称为根子群。</p><p>设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x27_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x28_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的极大理想，则<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x29_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是域。对每个<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x30_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，定义</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.21747-formula8"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x31_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x32_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>所在的模<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x33_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的同余类，则</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.21747-formula9"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x34_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>是环同态。设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x35_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，对每个<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x36_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>定义</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.21747-formula10"><label>. (*)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x37_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>则</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.21747-formula11"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x38_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>是群同态。对任意正整数<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x39_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x40_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，记</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x41_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>.</p><p>则同态核</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.21747-formula12"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x42_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>本文的主要结论如下：</p><p>定理1.1设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x43_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是含幺交换环，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x44_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，如果以下子群<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x45_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>与<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x46_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>生成<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x47_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x48_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>及其在<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x49_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>中的共轭都是<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x50_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的含根子群的极大子群。特别地，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x51_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>及其共轭是<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x52_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的含根子群的极大子群。</p><p>1)<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x53_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x54_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>,</p><p>2)<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x55_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x56_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x57_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>,</p><p>3)<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x58_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x59_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x60_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>.</p><p>定理1.2设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x61_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是含幺交换环，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x62_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x63_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的子群，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x64_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x65_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>中含根子群的极大子群，则<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x66_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是以下两种类型之一：</p><p>1) 存在<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x67_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的某个极大理想<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x68_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，使<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x69_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是域<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x70_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>上线性群<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x71_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的极大子群。当<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x72_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>时，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x73_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>一定是定理1的3类子群之一。</p><p>2) 对<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x74_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的每个极大理想都有</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x75_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>,</p><p>且<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x76_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x77_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的极大子群。</p></sec><sec id="s4"><title>2. 定理的证明</title><p>在定理1.1的证明中，我们要先用群同态<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x78_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>来映到域<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x79_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>上处理。所以我们先介绍域上的相关结论。从 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.21747-ref1">1</xref>] 定理1以及 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.21747-ref8">8</xref>] 定理3.6.1、3.7.2a容易得出以下引理。</p><p>引理2.1设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x80_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，如果以下子群<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x81_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>与<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x82_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>生成<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x83_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x84_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>及其在<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x85_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>中的共轭都是<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x86_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的含根子群的极大子群。特别的，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x87_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>及其共轭是<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x88_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的含根子群的极大子群。</p><p>1)<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x89_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x90_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>,</p><p>2)<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x91_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x92_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x93_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>,</p><p>3)<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x94_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x95_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>,<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x96_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>.</p><p>反过来，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x97_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>时，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x98_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>中不包含<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x99_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的任一含根子群的极大子群必为上面所列子群之一。</p><p>注记文献 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.21747-ref1">1</xref>] 定理1以及 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.21747-ref8">8</xref>] 定理3.7.2a中第2类极大子群中有两个例外情形，很显然两个例外情形不满足“<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x100_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>与<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x101_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>生成<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x102_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>”这一假设，不在我们讨论之列。</p><p>下面，我们依次来给出本文两个定理的证明。</p><p>定理1.1的证明设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x103_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x104_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的极大理想，定义<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x105_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>如(*)式，它的同态核<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x106_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x107_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的子群<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x108_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>真包含<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x109_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x110_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>真包含<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x111_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，由引理2.1知，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x112_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x113_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的极大子群，因此有</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x114_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>.</p><p>对每个<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x115_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，有</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x116_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>,</p><p>因而存在<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x117_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>使得</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x118_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>.</p><p>这时有</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x119_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>,</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x120_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>.</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x121_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>包含<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x122_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>及<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x123_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，从而包含它们的乘积<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x124_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，这说明了<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x125_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>中所有的<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x126_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。从而<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x127_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。这证明了<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x128_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x129_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的极大子群。</p><p>证毕。</p><p>定理1.2的证明设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x130_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x131_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的极大理想，定义<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x132_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>如(*)式，首先，考虑到<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x133_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的每个根子群</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.21747-formula13"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x134_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>在群同态<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x135_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>下的象为</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x136_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>,</p><p>它是<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x137_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的根子群。因此<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x138_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x139_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的含根子群的子群。如果存在<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x140_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的真子群<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x141_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>真包含<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x142_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.21747-formula14"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x143_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>是<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x144_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的真子群且真包含<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x145_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，与<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x146_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的极大性矛盾。</p><p>因此只有两种可能的情形：情形1.<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x147_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x148_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的极大子群；情形2.<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x149_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>情形1. 如果<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x150_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>不包含<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x151_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，此时<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x152_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>与<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x153_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>生成<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x154_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.21747-formula15"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x155_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>是<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x156_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的真子群且包含<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x157_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，与<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x158_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的极大性矛盾。因此，此时<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x159_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。当<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x160_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>时，由引理2.1知<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x161_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x162_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的3类极大子群之一，于是<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x163_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是定理1.1所说的3类子群之一。</p><p>情形2.<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x164_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>对每个<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x165_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，存在<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x166_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>使得</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x167_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>,</p><p>从而</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x168_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>,<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x169_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>.</p><p>如果<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x170_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则由<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x171_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>包含<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x172_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>及<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x173_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>可知<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x174_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>包含它们的乘积<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x175_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。这导致<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x176_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，与<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x177_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x178_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的极大子群矛盾。因此<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x179_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>不能包含<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x180_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x181_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x182_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的真子群。如果存在<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x183_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的真子群<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x184_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>真包含<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x185_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x186_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x187_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的真子群且真包含<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x188_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，与<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x189_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的极大性矛盾。这迫使<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x190_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x191_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的极大子群。</p><p>证毕。</p><p>注记我们猜想情形2中<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x192_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的极大子群<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x193_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>具有以下形式：</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x194_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>,</p><p>其中，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x195_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x196_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>中真包含于<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-1250555x197_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的某个极大理想。此结论有待探究。</p></sec><sec id="s5"><title>文章引用</title><p>侯 欣,李尚志.